    "description": "《蜜蜂在哪里酿蜜》通过成年人的视角回顾了儿时的几段记忆。<br><br>游戏过程仿佛发生在怀旧的梦里一般，别致、古怪而又意味深长。游戏再现了美好的童年，无忧无虑，无拘无束，开开心心地玩过家家就好，不用为生活而忧虑。<br><br>《蜜蜂在哪里酿蜜》是一款解谜冒险类游戏，不过随着游戏的推进，游戏操作会有所变化。主人公桑妮通过成人的角度回顾童年的时候，游戏采用第一人称视角。这一转变发生在她的工作场所，她最终也要在这里决定自己人生之后的方向。<br><br>游戏通过插曲游戏实现四季交替，这样可以突出叙事元素，同时加强玩家的代入感。插曲游戏可令玩家从四季流转的时间角度体验这款游戏，每一个季节、插曲和每一段记忆的挖法各不相同。<br><br>建议使用Xbox One手柄等同类设备，游戏启动之后会完全支持此类设备。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1001640/extras/d760c2d33ed212d4f7ae2a7bea31fb89.avif?t=1680723786\" width=680 height=342 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1001640/extras/86fdab11c65828e596ba0124c7c07e5b.poster.avif?t=1680723786\" width=680 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1001640/extras/86fdab11c65828e596ba0124c7c07e5b.webm?t=1680723786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1001640/extras/86fdab11c65828e596ba0124c7c07e5b.mp4?t=1680723786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1001640/extras/8175df36704fdfcec6c76b7401470361.poster.avif?t=1680723786\" width=680 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1001640/extras/8175df36704fdfcec6c76b7401470361.webm?t=1680723786\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1001640/extras/8175df36704fdfcec6c76b7401470361.mp4?t=1680723786\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/stor